source:
TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_SEQ_00Uin Nee is wrestling with the concept of swings.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung
Die Schwierigkeit des Auftrags wird an die aktuelle Stufe angepasst und die Klasse (der Job) darf nicht gewechselt werden.

Uin Nee möchte eine Traumschaukel bauen.

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_TODO_00<tab>Slay fibrous psammeads at the destination and obtain psammead silk.
TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the psammead silk to Uin Nee.
TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_000<tab>Nothing makes me pity your kind quite like swings. After all, who needs a silly contraption like that when you can fly?
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_000<tab>Ich hab neulich eine Schaukel gesehen! Wir Pixies kämen nie auf die Idee, auf einem Brett hin und her zu schwingen. Wir können ja fliegen!

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Yet you...you have to tie a piece of wood to a tree branch and hope that it doesn't snap, dropping you to the ground and killing you instantly! All for the chance to go higher, and higher, and feel like you're about to take flight. But you won't! It's depressing, is what it is.
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Aber die Kinder haben offensichtlich große Freude daran. Da wird mir mal wieder klar, wie bedauernswert es ist, keine Flügel zu haben.

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_002<tab>The children do seem to like them, though. And if they want a sad simulacrum of flight, who am I to refuse? In any case, I have a tree and this piece of wood I picked up off of the ground, so I've practically built the entire thing already!
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_002<tab>Also hab ich mir vorgenommen, eine Schaukel für die Kinder zu basteln. Sie sollen erfahren, wie schön es in der Luft ist!

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_003<tab>All that we need is rope! Strong rope, preferably. Falling to your death is no fun at all, even if it <var 1A 02 /var>is<var 1A 01 /var> a dream. Maybe you could get me some of that sturdy psammead silk everyone raves about? Pretty please?
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_003<tab>Ein Holzbrett hab ich schon besorgt. Jetzt brauche ich nur noch ein passendes Seil dazu. Kannst du mir bitte <var 32 ((EventItem)) 02F61E9004020502 /var> besorgen?

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_004<tab>It's the big, nasty mother psammeads that have the strongest silk. They're always a bit reluctant to come out of hiding, but fortunately, they'll come scuttling if you attack the smaller ones!
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_004<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F223D4030502 /var>)) /var> findest du bestimmt hier ganz in der Nähe. Erlege so viele, bis du ein richtig starkes Exemplar erwischt hast!

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_010<tab>How are the psammeads? Still crawly and unsettling?

TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_011<tab>Oh, yes! This should be more than strong enough. I'll have to trick some mature mortals into testing it first, of course. Wouldn't want to risk the children! Once it's properly spun into the dream, maybe I'll even give it a try myself!
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_011<tab>Ah ja! Der dürfte stabil genug sein. Ich werde den Faden gleich an das Brett knüpfen, einen Zauber darauf wirken und fertig ist die Traumschaukel!

source: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_012<tab>I admit, the thought of being gently rocked is somehow soothing. Back and forth, back and forth... If I close my eyes, I can almost remember...
target: TEXT_BANPIX127_03715_UINNEE_000_012<tab>Die Vorstellung, sanft hin und her bewegt zu werden, ist irgendwie beruhigend. Hin und her<var 1D /var>... Hin und her<var 1D /var>... Es kommt mir so<var 1D /var>... bekannt vor<var 1D /var>...
